

###  _cd_ to _deploy_ folder
``` cd deploy ```

### Connect to cluster
```gcloud container clusters get-credentials prod-cluster-01 --zone us-west1-b --project production-228907```



# Deploy in Production cluster

### Deploy platform-registry-api
```helm --set "global.env=prod" upgrade --install platformregistryapi platformregistryapi```





#Deploy in staging and dev clusters

Dev :
	- helm --set "global.env=dev" upgrade --install platformregistryapi --name=platformregistryapi

Stage :
	- helm --set "global.env=staging" upgrade --install platformregistryapi --name=platformregistryapi
